    "description": "Gaurs Group Advisory Limited is actively seeking a talented and motivated Real Estate Agent to join our dynamic team in Tiruchirappalli. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Gaurs Group Advisory Limited:\nGaurs Group Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Gaurs Group Advisory Limited!",
